<div id=3D"outline-container-orgf027c0f" class=3D"outline-3">
<h3 id=3D"orgf027c0f">Etienne Marais announced</h3>
<div class=3D"outline-text-3" id=3D"text-orgf027c0f">
<p>
Hi Dune enthusiasts!  :camel:=20=20
</p>

<p>
We will hold our regular Dune dev meeting tomorrow, on <b>Wednesday, Octobe=
r, 2nd at 16:00 CET</b>. As usual, the session will be one hour long.
</p>

<p>
Whether you are a maintainer, a regular contributor, a new joiner or just c=
urious, you are welcome to join: these discussions are opened! The goal of =
these meetings is to provide a place to discuss the ongoing work together a=
nd synchronise between the Dune developers :smile:
</p>
</div>

